= Publications
Selected research publications and public research artifacts.

== Recent Publications

- *Optimizing CUDA like a Human: Micro-Profiling Tools as Expert Surrogates for LLM-Based GPU Kernel Optimization.* Jiading Gai, Shuai Zhang, Kaj Bostrom, Jin Huang, Vihang Patil, Haoyang Fang, Bernie Wang, Huzefa Rangwala, and George Karypis. Submitted to Transactions on Machine Learning Research, 2026. [https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.26453 paper] [https://arxiv.org/pdf/2606.26453 pdf] [https://openreview.net/attachment?id=yWtLQ5iMrL&name=supplementary_material supplement]

- *DualKV: Shared-Prompt Flash Attention for Efficient RL Training with Large Rollouts and Long Contexts.* Jiading Gai, Shuai Zhang, Xiang Song, Bernie Wang, and George Karypis. arXiv preprint, 2026. [https://arxiv.org/abs/2605.15422 paper] [https://arxiv.org/pdf/2605.15422 pdf] [https://github.com/amazon-science/dualkv-flash-attn-for-rl code]

- *HetRL: Efficient Reinforcement Learning for LLMs in Heterogeneous Environments.* Yongjun He, Shuai Zhang, Jiading Gai, Xiyuan Zhang, Boran Han, Bernie Wang, Huzefa Rangwala, and George Karypis. Proceedings of Machine Learning and Systems, 2026. MLSys 2026 Oral. [https://arxiv.org/abs/2512.12476 paper]

